      "content": "that's a pretty heavy assumption. are you saying the instability in an urban environment actually makes the person more dangerous or likely to reoffend compared to someone in the suburbs, even if the crime is exactly the same? it feels like youre implying that the environment itself is a predictor of criminality.",
